**Cursed Civilian** | Townsfolk Miscellaneous 
__Basics__
If the Cursed Civilian is attacked by a lycan or a werewolf, they will turn into a wolf instead of dying.
__Details__
The Cursed Civilian is part of the townsfolk team, however they may betray their team at some point. The Cursed Civilian believes they are a citizen, but still appears in the rolelist as a Cursed Civilian.
If attacked any other way than by a lycan or a werewolf, the Cursed Civilian will die as usual.
